<h3>One-way binding + action</h3>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p>You can pass a binding into the panel, but to respect non-mutation, the panel will never change your binding.</p>
    <p>Use the <code>didToggle</code> action to respond to a user clicking your panel.</p>
    <p>
      {{#let (get-code-snippet "open-binding.hbs") as |snippet|}}
        <pre class={{snippet.language}}>
          {{snippet.source}}
        </pre>
      {{/let}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6">
{{!-- BEGIN-SNIPPET open-binding --}}
<button {{action 'toggleIsOpen'}} class="btn btn-default u-margin-bottom">Toggle</button>

<span>isOpen: {{this.isOpen}}</span>


<CpPanel @click={{action "toggleIsOpen"}} @open={{this.isOpen}} as |p|>
  <p.toggle>
    <p>Click me!</p>
  </p.toggle>
